# Karate Fork (j8d-org/karate)

This is a fork of [karatelabs/karate](https://github.com/karatelabs/karate) maintained by j8d-org.

## Purpose

This fork contains GraalVM version upgrades needed for compatibility with the karate-debug project's polyglot debugging features.

## Git Remotes

- `origin` - Upstream karatelabs/karate (read-only reference)
- `j8d-org` - Our fork at j8d-org/karate (push here)

## Creating PRs Within This Fork

GitHub's default PR behavior targets the upstream repo. To create a PR within this fork:

```bash
gh pr create --repo j8d-org/karate --base master --head <branch-name> --title "PR Title"
```

Or merge directly to master for simple changes:

```bash
git checkout master
git merge <branch-name>
git push j8d-org master
```

## Tagging Releases

When creating a new release tag:

```bash
git tag v1.5.2-j8d.X
git push j8d-org v1.5.2-j8d.X
```

The tag format is `v{karate-version}-j8d.{patch}` where patch increments for each change we make.

